# FastAPI Assignment 2

## Project Title

Product API using FastAPI

## Description

This project demonstrates the use of FastAPI to build a simple REST API for managing product data.
The API allows users to retrieve product information and filter products using query parameters.

## Technologies Used

* Python
* FastAPI
* Pydantic
* Uvicorn

## Project Structure

Assignment2/
│
├── main.py
│   ├── output1.png
│   ├── output2.png
│
└── README.md

## Features

* Create API endpoints using FastAPI
* Retrieve product data
* Filter products using query parameters
* Automatic API documentation using Swagger UI

## How to Run the Project

1. Install required libraries

```
pip install fastapi uvicorn
```

2. Run the FastAPI server

```
uvicorn main:app --reload
```

3. Open the browser and go to:

```
http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs
```

This will open the Swagger UI where you can test the API endpoints.

## Output

The screenshots contains the output  of the API responses.

